<p>To characterize the change in moisture stress, we calculated temporal trends in maximum cumulative water deficit (MCWD—Aragão et al., 
 <xref rid="gcb14413-bib-0002" ref-type="ref">2007</xref>) for each plot. MCWD represents the most negative value of water deficit (wd), that is, the difference between precipitation (
 <italic>P</italic>) and evapotranspiration (
 <italic>E</italic>) within each year, where for each month (
 <italic>n</italic>) wd is quantified as: 
 <disp-formula id="gcb14413-disp-0001">
  <label>(1)</label>
  <math id="nlm-math-1">
   <mrow>
    <mrow>
     <mtable>
      <mtr>
       <mtd/>
       <mtd columnalign="left">
        <mrow>
         <mi mathvariant="normal">If</mi>
         <mspace width="0.166667em"/>
         <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">wd</mi>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
           <mo>−</mo>
           <mn>1</mn>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <mo>−</mo>
         <msub>
          <mi>E</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <msub>
          <mi>P</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo>&lt;</mo>
         <mn>0</mn>
         <mo>;</mo>
        </mrow>
       </mtd>
      </mtr>
      <mtr>
       <mtd/>
       <mtd columnalign="left">
        <mrow>
         <mi mathvariant="normal">then</mi>
         <mspace width="0.277778em"/>
         <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">wd</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo>=</mo>
         <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">wd</mi>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
           <mo>−</mo>
           <mn>1</mn>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <mo>−</mo>
         <msub>
          <mi>E</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <msub>
          <mi>P</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
         </msub>
        </mrow>
       </mtd>
      </mtr>
      <mtr>
       <mtd/>
       <mtd columnalign="left">
        <mrow>
         <mi mathvariant="normal">else</mi>
         <mspace width="0.166667em"/>
         <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">wd</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo>=</mo>
         <mn>0</mn>
        </mrow>
       </mtd>
      </mtr>
     </mtable>
    </mrow>
    <mo>.</mo>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>
</p>
